It is painted in a metallic silver color, which reflects light and gives it a sleek appearance. The Ford emblem is centrally located at the top center of the grille. It is a circular shape with a raised, three-dimensional design. The emblem itself is a dark blue or black color, contrasting sharply with the silver background of the grille. The Ford logo is prominently displayed, making it easily recognizable as part of the Ford brand identity.

The grille's size is substantial, covering a large area of the front bumper and extending slightly upward towards the hood. This size contributes to the robust and commanding presence of the vehicle. The overall design of the grille is clean and modern, aligning well with the Expedition's luxurious and powerful aesthetic.
